<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('components/head.ejs'); -%>
    <title>Covaccine Scheduler</title>
    <style>
      .button {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px;
        position: relative;
        right: -40%;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 1000px) {
        .button {
          right: 0%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="text-align: center">
    <%- include('components/header.ejs'); -%>

    <div class="home">
      <div class="text left">
        <h1>Get your Vaccination Appointment Number and Date</h1>
        <a class="card icon-box button" href="/register"
          ><h3><i>Register</i></h3></a
        >
      </div>
      <img class="img right" src="/img/covid.png" alt="covid" />
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <div class="info">
      <!-- <span>About</span> -->
      <p>
        <em>Covaccine Scheduler</em> is the digital solution for vaccination drive, it
        doesn't work on first come, first serve idea, rather it works on the
        idea "who needs vaccination first?". <br />
        Vaccination drive will be phase-wise, details of which are described
        below. <br />
         <strong> Phase 1 </strong> <br />
          Healthcare Personnel. Frontline essential employees working in various
          government departments. <br>
          <strong> Phase 2 </strong> <br />
          People aged 75 years or above because they are at high risk of
          hospitalization, illness, and death due to COVID-19. <br>
          <strong> Phase 3 </strong> <br />
          People aged 65—74 years because they are at high risk of
          hospitalization, illness, and death due to COVID-19. <br>
          <strong> Phase 4 </strong> <br />
          People aged 16—64 years with underlying medical conditions which
          increase the risk of serious, life-threatening complications from
          COVID-19. <br>
          <strong> Phase 5 </strong> <br>
          Other essential workers, such as people who work in transportation and
          logistics, food service, housing construction and finance, information
          technology, communications, energy, law, media, public safety, and
          public health. <br>
          <strong> Phase 6 </strong> <br>
          Rest of the citizens.
      </p>
    </div>
    <br />
    <%- include('components/footer.ejs'); -%>

    <!--JavaScript - Bootstrap Bundle with Popper -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ygbV9kiqUc6oa4msXn9868pTtWMgiQaeYH7/t7LECLbyPA2x65Kgf80OJFdroafW"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
